      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DOONGALLA GEM (1) finished well back at Healesville last time when a 5.5 lengths sixth (17.16) but scored three back at Shepparton (25.43). The form out of her last race has been franked. Has winning claims on her best figures. PATRIOT NIAMH (8) hit the ground running from a squeeze draw and prominent early but run ended and faded to finish 6th at this track in Grade 5 company. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from four starts. Worth following up. UNIVERSE (2) was out of the placings last time when fifth at Shepparton (26.20) but scored four back at Shepparton (22.01). Expected to give a good account. HAPPY AND NUMB (3) cannot be underestimated.",
